David Bazan (; born January 22, 1976) is an American indie rock singer-songwriter from Phoenix, Arizona who now resides in Seattle, Washington.
In early 2006, he began performing and recording under his own name.
In late 2017 he returned to playing under the Pedro the Lion name.
